DOC.TE:
   In both eras, Merrick's new friends, and his successful uncle and
sponsor, Gilbert Hawking, propel the activity. Things move fast;
though some details may surprise, they do not halt the action.

   Materials needed: small rectangular meat tray; tape; 3 straws; 2
bamboo skewers; 4 lids from 35-millimeter film canisters; balloon;
some help from an adult.

   European team: Darren Clarke, Northern Ireland; Thomas Bjorn,
Denmark; Padraig Harrington, Ireland; Colin Montgomerie, Scotland;
Pierre Fulke, Sweden; Lee Westwood, England; Niclas Fasth, Sweden;
Paul McGinley, Ireland; Bernhard Langer, Germany; Phillip Price,
Wales; c-Sergio Garcia, Spain; c-Jesper Parnevik, Sweden. Captain:
Sam Torrance, Scotland.
